c("Preheat oven to 350 degrees.", "Spread oats, cereal and sesame seeds in a 13\" x 9\"  nonstick jelly roll pan.", "Bake, stirring occasionally, until oats are toasted,  about 15 minutes.", "Meanwhile, chop apricots (use the food processor); transfer to a large bowl.", "Add raisins, protein powder and wheat germ; toss with hands to  mix.", "Lightly coat jelly roll pan with cooking spray.", "In a heavy saucepan over  medium-high heat, combine rice syrup and sugar; bring to  a boil.", "Reduce heat to  low, stir in peanut butter, vanilla and cinnamon.", 
