c("Preheat barbecue to medium heat. Place chicken in a large, sealable plastic bag.", "In a bowl, stir together oil, lemon juice, vinegar, basil, garlic, mustard, sugar and ground pepper.", "Pour half the mixture over the chicken.", "Seal plastic bag, pressing out excess air, and refrigerate at least 30 minutes.", "Save the remaining marinade to baste the chicken during grilling.", "Meanwhile, grill whole red peppers on barbecue until skin is blackened on all sides.", "Place peppers in a paper bag, fold shut and let cool 10 minutes.", 
