c("Preheat oven to 375 degrees.", "Heat large nonstick skillet over medium high heat. Brown beef until no  longer pink.", "Drain.", "Saute onions,  oregano and garlic for 5 minutes.", "Add wine through tomatoes (7 ingredients),  and bring to a boil.", "Reduce heat, and simmer 10 minutes or until thick.", "Combine flour, milk, and 1/4 tsp. nutmeg in medium saucepan and bring to  boil.", "Reduce heat, and cook  for 7 minutes or until thick, stirring constantly.", "Remove milk mixture from  heat.   Stir in feta cheese, half of Parmesan cheese and eggs.", 
